        <p class="mod-desc">Build the mental model every cloud practitioner needs. Understand how cloud providers work, what you pay for, and why cloud has replaced on-premise infrastructure in modern engineering.</p>
        <ul class="mod-learns">
          <li>IaaS, PaaS &amp; SaaS service models explained</li>
          <li>Cloud economics: CapEx vs OpEx, pay-as-you-go</li>
          <li>AWS global infrastructure: Regions &amp; Availability Zones</li>
          <li>Shared Responsibility Model &amp; compliance basics</li>
          <li>AWS Management Console, CLI &amp; SDK overview</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="mod-footer">
          <span class="mod-duration">⏱ Weeks 1–2 · ~8 hrs</span>
          <span class="mod-level">Beginner</span>
        </div>
      </div>

