        <p class="mod-desc">Get hands on with the services that power 70% of cloud workloads. Launch EC2 instances, configure secure networks, store objects in S3, and lock everything down with IAM.</p>
        <ul class="mod-learns">
          <li>EC2: instance types, AMIs, user-data, key pairs</li>
          <li>S3: buckets, policies, versioning &amp; static hosting</li>
          <li>VPC: subnets, route tables, internet &amp; NAT gateways</li>
          <li>Security Groups &amp; NACLs for layered defence</li>
          <li>IAM: users, roles, policies &amp; least-privilege design</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="mod-footer">
          <span class="mod-duration">⏱ Weeks 3–4 · ~10 hrs</span>
          <span class="mod-level">Intermediate</span>
        </div>
      </div>

