          <div class="mod-ico">🐳</div>
          <div><span class="mod-num">Phase 3</span><div class="mod-name">Docker &amp; Containerisation on AWS</div></div>
        </div>
        <p class="mod-desc">Package your applications once, run them anywhere. Master Docker from first principles and integrate containers natively into the AWS ecosystem using ECR and ECS.</p>
        <ul class="mod-learns">
          <li>Docker architecture: images, containers &amp; volumes</li>
          <li>Writing production-grade Dockerfiles &amp; .dockerignore</li>
          <li>Docker Compose for multi-container local dev</li>
          <li>Amazon ECR: building, tagging &amp; pushing images</li>
          <li>Introduction to ECS &amp; Fargate for managed containers</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="mod-footer">
          <span class="mod-duration">⏱ Weeks 5–6 · ~10 hrs</span>
          <span class="mod-level">Intermediate</span>
        </div>
