        </div>
        <p class="mod-desc">Take real applications live. Configure Nginx as a reverse proxy on EC2, automate SSL with Let's Encrypt, build serverless APIs with Lambda, and connect services with event-driven patterns.</p>
        <ul class="mod-learns">
          <li>Nginx reverse proxy &amp; virtual host configuration</li>
          <li>SSL/TLS with Certbot + Let's Encrypt on EC2</li>
          <li>Route 53: DNS, A/CNAME records &amp; health checks</li>
